Token.Abstract: Provides extensions to NSDictionary for various common tasks.
Returns a new dictionary that contains a dictionary for a form encoded string.

Parameter.Name: encodedString
Parameter.Abstract: A string of form encoded compontents.

ReturnValue.Abstract: A new dictionary that contains a dictionary for the form encoded string, or nil if encodedString is an invalid representation of a dictionary.

Token.Abstract: Returns a string of form encoded components for using as the query string in a URL.

ReturnValue.Abstract: A string of form encoded compontents.

Token.Abstract: Returns the object returned by mutableCopyWithZone: where the zone is nil.

ReturnValue.Abstract: The object returned by the NSMutableCopying protocol method mutableCopyWithZone:, where the zone is nil.

Token.Abstract: Returns a string of the MD5 sum of the receiver.

ReturnValue.Abstract: The string of the MD5 sum of the receiver.

Token.Abstract: Returns a string of the SHA1 sum of the receiver.

ReturnValue.Abstract: The string of the SHA1 sum of the receiver.
